---
date: 
  created: {{ end_date.isoformat() }}
description: "{{ posts|length }} posts from {{ start_date }} to {{ end_date }}"
hide:
  - navigation
  - toc
---

# {% if logo_url %}<img src="{{ logo_url }}" alt="" style="height:1.2em;vertical-align:middle"> {% endif %}{{ feed_name }} Digest — {{ week_id }}

Posts from **{{ start_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') }}** to **{{ end_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') }}**. Total: **{{ posts|length }}** posts.

<!-- more -->

---

{% for post in posts %}
<div class="bsky-card" markdown="1">

<div class="bsky-header" markdown="1">
{% if post.author_avatar %}
<img src="{{ post.author_avatar }}" class="bsky-avatar">
{% endif %}
<div class="bsky-author-meta" markdown="1">
**{{ post.author_name }}** [@{{ post.author_handle }}]({{ post.bsky_url }}) · {{ post.date }}
</div>
</div>

<div class="bsky-content" markdown="1">

{{ post.text }}

{% if post.embed_images %}
{% for img in post.embed_images %}
![{{ img.alt|e }}]({{ img.url }})
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

</div>

<div class="bsky-footer" markdown="1">

:material-heart: {{ post.likes }} &nbsp;&nbsp; :material-repeat: {{ post.reposts }} &nbsp;&nbsp; :material-comment: {{ post.replies }}

[:material-open-in-new: View on Bluesky]({{ post.bsky_url }}){ .md-button .md-button--primary }

</div>
</div>

---
{% endfor %}